&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n手足前手足後<br />\n但吹風罷工冇可能<br />\n你知唔知推一個行動係好唔容易<br />\n你一個潑冷水post分分鐘就推走咗幾個想參與既人<br />\n<br />\n出post前用腦諗清楚先！"},{"pid":"402d39b2252c8e332bcf063426710b8eb079abf5","tid":1739171,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n另外，一番肺腑連同深度分析，大家都可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1</a>"}]}